(11, 'popularity', '1', 'What are the most popular regions for real estate investment in Turkey?', 'The most popular regions for real estate investment in Turkey include Istanbul, Antalya, and Bodrum. These regions offer a wide variety of properties and have a growing tourism industry, which can lead to high rental income.', '1', '1', NULL, '2023-02-01 10:18:42', '2023-02-01 10:18:42'),
(25, NULL, '1', 'Can foreigners buy property in Turkey?', 'Yes, foreigners can buy property in Turkey. However, they are subject to the same laws and regulations as Turkish citizens.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2023-02-01 10:43:44', '2023-02-01 10:45:51'),
(26, NULL, '1', 'How do I obtain financing for a property in Turkey?', 'To obtain financing for a property in Turkey, you can apply for a mortgage through a Turkish bank. However, as a foreign investor, you may face stricter lending criteria and higher interest rates.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2023-02-01 10:46:45', '2023-02-01 10:47:32'),
(27, NULL, '1', 'What types of properties are available in Turkey?', 'Properties available in Turkey include apartments, villas, commercial properties, and land for development.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2023-02-01 10:47:51', '2023-02-01 10:47:51'),
(28, NULL, '1', 'Are there any restrictions on property ownership for foreigners in Turkey?', 'There are restrictions on property ownership for foreigners in certain border regions. These restrictions are put in place for security reasons and can vary depending on the location.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2023-02-01 10:48:13', '2023-02-01 10:48:13'),
(29, NULL, '1', 'What are the taxes and fees associated with buying property in Turkey?', 'The taxes and fees associated with buying property in Turkey include a value-added tax, a stamp duty, and a title deed fee.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2023-02-01 10:48:26', '2023-02-01 10:48:26'),
(30, NULL, '1', 'What is the process for obtaining a residence permit in Turkey?', 'The process for obtaining a residence permit in Turkey includes showing proof of property ownership and providing the necessary documentation.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2023-02-01 10:48:44', '2023-02-01 10:48:44'),
(31, NULL, '1', 'Can I rent out my property in Turkey?', 'Yes, you can rent out your property in Turkey. However, it\'s important to ensure that the property is in compliance with all necessary regulations and laws.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2023-02-01 10:48:59', '2023-02-01 10:48:59'),
(32, NULL, '1', 'Are there any incentives or benefits for foreign investors in Turkey?', 'Yes, there are incentives and benefits for foreign investors in Turkey such as citizenship by investment options, tax exemptions, and subsidies.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2023-02-01 10:49:14', '2023-02-01 10:49:14'),
(33, NULL, '1', 'How can I ensure that my real estate investment in Turkey is secure and profitable?', 'To ensure that your real estate investment in Turkey is secure and profitable, it\'s important to conduct thorough research, seek professional advice, and work with a reputable company like Nomar Invest. Nomar Invest can assist you throughout the buying process, and provide legal and financial advice to ensure that your investment is secure and profitable.', '1', NULL, NULL, '2023-02-01 10:49:29', '2023-02-01 10:49:29'),
(34, NULL, '2', 'Research the market:', 'Before investing in real estate in Turkey, it\'s important to conduct thorough market research to understand the current trends, prices, and potential areas for growth. This includes researching the different regions of Turkey, as well as the types of properties available and their corresponding prices. Nomar Invest offers a wide variety of properties in various locations throughout Turkey, such as Istanbul, Antalya, and Bodrum, making it easy for investors to find the right property to align with their goals.', '1', NULL, '1', '2023-02-01 12:35:26', '2023-03-13 21:25:42'),
(35, NULL, '2', 'Hire a local real estate agent:', 'Hiring a local real estate agent with experience in the Turkish market will be helpful in finding the right property and navigating the legal and cultural aspects of the buying process. Nomar Invest has a team of experienced local agents who are knowledgeable about the market and can assist investors throughout the buying process.', '1', NULL, '2', '2023-02-01 12:43:37', '2023-03-13 21:25:31'),
(36, NULL, '2', 'Choose a property', 'After researching the market and working with a local agent, choose a property that aligns with your investment goals. This could be a residential property, a commercial property, or even land for development. Nomar Invest offers a wide variety of properties, including apartments, villas, commercial properties and lands, making it easy for investors to find the right property to align with their goals.', '1', NULL, '3', '2023-02-01 12:45:23', '2023-03-13 21:25:21'),
(37, NULL, '2', 'Obtain financing:', 'If you need financing for your investment, consider obtaining a mortgage from a Turkish bank. It is important to note that as a foreigner, you may face stricter lending criteria and higher interest rates. Nomar Invest can assist investors in obtaining financing through Turkish banks, and provide guidance on the loan application process.', '1', NULL, '4', '2023-02-01 12:46:07', '2023-03-13 21:25:11'),
(38, NULL, '2', 'Complete the purchase:', 'Once you\'ve found the right property and obtained financing, complete the purchase by signing a sales contract and paying the purchase price. It is important to have a lawyer review all legal documents before signing. Nomar Invest can provide legal representation and assist with the documentation process to ensure a smooth transaction.', '1', NULL, '5', '2023-02-01 12:46:30', '2023-03-13 21:25:02'),
(39, NULL, '2', 'Obtain a residence permit:', 'As a foreign investor in Turkey, you will need to obtain a residence permit in order to legally reside in the country. This can be done by showing proof of property ownership and providing the necessary documentation. Nomar Invest can assist with this process and ensure that all necessary documentation is in order.', '1', NULL, '6', '2023-02-01 12:47:33', '2023-03-13 21:24:19'),
(40, NULL, '2', 'Manage and maintain the property:', 'After purchasing the property, it\'s important to manage and maintain it in order to ensure its value is preserved and to generate rental income. This can include hiring a property management company, and making necessary repairs and renovations. Nomar Invest offers property management services to assist investors in managing and maintaining their properties, including rent collection, tenant screening, and maintenance.', '1', NULL, '7', '2023-02-01 12:47:46', '2023-03-13 21:24:09'),
(41, NULL, '2', 'Consider property management:', 'If you are not planning to reside in Turkey and are looking to generate rental income from your property, it is highly recommended to consider hiring a property management company to handle the day-to-day management of your property, including rent collection, tenant screening, and maintenance. Nomar Invest\'s property management services can help ensure that your property is well-maintained and generates a steady rental income.', '1', NULL, '8', '2023-02-01 12:48:04', '2023-03-13 21:23:59'),
(42, NULL, '2', 'Keep your documents:', 'Keep all your document in a safe place, as you will need them for tax filing and also for any legal issues. Nomar Invest can assist in keeping your documents organized and ensuring', '1', NULL, '9', '2023-02-01 12:48:29', '2023-03-13 21:23:48'),
(43, NULL, '2', 'Seek legal and financial advice:', 'Seek legal and financial advice: Seek legal and financial advice from a professional with experience in the Turkish real estate market to ensure that your investment is secure and to navigate any potential legal or financial challenges. Nomar Invest\'s team of experts includes lawyers and financial advisors who can provide guidance and advice on any legal or financial matters related to your investment.', '1', NULL, '10', '2023-02-01 12:48:45', '2023-03-13 21:23:37');

