INSERT INTO `page_translations` (`id`, `page_id`, `title`, `locale`, `content`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 1, 'Turkish Citizenship', 'en', '<section class=\"container mb-2 mb-xl-5 pb-lg-4\"><!-- Inline steps: Vertical -->\r\n<div class=\"steps steps-vertical\">\r\n<div class=\"step active\">\r\n<div class=\"step-progress\"><span class=\"step-number\">1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"step-label\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 pb-1\">Research the market:</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">Before investing in real estate in Turkey, it\'s important to conduct thorough market research to understand the current trends, prices, and potential areas for growth. This includes researching the different regions of Turkey, as well as the types of properties available and their corresponding prices. Nomar Invest offers a wide variety of properties in various locations throughout Turkey, such as Istanbul, Antalya, and Bodrum, making it easy for investors to find the right property to align with their goals.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"step active\">\r\n<div class=\"step-progress\"><span class=\"step-number\">2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"step-label\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 pb-1\">Hire a local real estate agent:</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">Hiring a local real estate agent with experience in the Turkish market will be helpful in finding the right property and navigating the legal and cultural aspects of the buying process. Nomar Invest has a team of experienced local agents who are knowledgeable about the market and can assist investors throughout the buying process.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"step active\">\r\n<div class=\"step-progress\"><span class=\"step-number\">3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"step-label\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 pb-1\">Choose a property</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">After researching the market and working with a local agent, choose a property that aligns with your investment goals. This could be a residential property, a commercial property, or even land for development. Nomar Invest offers a wide variety of properties, including apartments, villas, commercial properties and lands, making it easy for investors to find the right property to align with their goals.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"step active\">\r\n<div class=\"step-progress\"><span class=\"step-number\">4</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"step-label\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 pb-1\">Obtain financing:</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">If you need financing for your investment, consider obtaining a mortgage from a Turkish bank. It is important to note that as a foreigner, you may face stricter lending criteria and higher interest rates. Nomar Invest can assist investors in obtaining financing through Turkish banks, and provide guidance on the loan application process.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"step active\">\r\n<div class=\"step-progress\"><span class=\"step-number\">5</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"step-label\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 pb-1\">Complete the purchase:</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">Once you\'ve found the right property and obtained financing, complete the purchase by signing a sales contract and paying the purchase price. It is important to have a lawyer review all legal documents before signing. Nomar Invest can provide legal representation and assist with the documentation process to ensure a smooth transaction.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"step active\">\r\n<div class=\"step-progress\"><span class=\"step-number\">6</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"step-label\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 pb-1\">Obtain a residence permit:</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">As a foreign investor in Turkey, you will need to obtain a residence permit in order to legally reside in the country. This can be done by showing proof of property ownership and providing the necessary documentation. Nomar Invest can assist with this process and ensure that all necessary documentation is in order.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"step active\">\r\n<div class=\"step-progress\"><span class=\"step-number\">7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"step-label\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 pb-1\">Manage and maintain the property:</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">After purchasing the property, it\'s important to manage and maintain it in order to ensure its value is preserved and to generate rental income. This can include hiring a property management company, and making necessary repairs and renovations. Nomar Invest offers property management services to assist investors in managing and maintaining their properties, including rent collection, tenant screening, and maintenance.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"step active\">\r\n<div class=\"step-progress\"><span class=\"step-number\">8</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"step-label\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 pb-1\">Consider property management:</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">If you are not planning to reside in Turkey and are looking to generate rental income from your property, it is highly recommended to consider hiring a property management company to handle the day-to-day management of your property, including rent collection, tenant screening, and maintenance. Nomar Invest\'s property management services can help ensure that your property is well-maintained and generates a steady rental income.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"step active\">\r\n<div class=\"step-progress\"><span class=\"step-number\">9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"step-label\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 pb-1\">Keep your documents:</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">Keep all your document in a safe place, as you will need them for tax filing and also for any legal issues. Nomar Invest can assist in keeping your documents organized and ensuring</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"step active\">\r\n<div class=\"step-progress\"><span class=\"step-number\">10</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"step-label\">\r\n<h5 class=\"mb-2 pb-1\">Seek legal and financial advice:</h5>\r\n<p class=\"mb-0\">Seek legal and financial advice: Seek legal and financial advice from a professional with experience in the Turkish real estate market to ensure that your investment is secure and to naviga