te any potential legal or financial challenges. Nomar Invest\'s team of experts includes lawyers and financial advisors who can provide guidance and advice on any legal or financial matters related to your investment.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', 'Turkish Citizenship by Investment Programme You can be a Turkish Citizen by purchasing a property in Turkey that is worth a minimum of $400,000. The Spouse and childen who are less than 18 years old will also be granted Turkish Citizenship. Your Turkish Citizenship will remain throughout your life and your childen will be born as Turkish Citizens. You can keep multiple citizenship along with your Turkish Citizenship.', '2023-03-31 22:48:37', '2023-03-31 22:48:37');
