(103, 94, 'en', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: widow-orphan lines-together; page-break-after: avoid; mso-outline-level: 2; margin: 2.0pt 0in 0in 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #2f5496; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">Overview of the Project</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">We can say that by reaching this project, you have arrived at your dream home with all that the word means. It is the house that combines all the luxury of living, social services, and unique designs in one place, with a new lifestyle that combines all the services you need in one place. In addition to being in one of the historic European areas of Istanbul that tourists from all over the world visit, the Topkapi area is considered one of the rich historical areas due to the presence of many historical and archaeological landmarks that give it a distinctive character from other areas in Istanbul. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">It is also one of the closest areas to the city centre, as it falls under the Fatih Municipality, which includes more than 20 museums, 300 mosques, and religious landmarks. You will find a high quality of life everywhere around you within this project when it comes to services. You will find green spaces that give you a moment to meet with nature and renew your energy, and you will find educational services that provide a high-quality education and rank on the local and international level. All of this will give you a sense of stability and prosperity that was once just a dream. You will see and live it with us in this project.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: widow-orphan lines-together; page-break-after: avoid; mso-outline-level: 2; margin: 2.0pt 0in 0in 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #2f5496; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">Project Features</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: 8.0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: 0in; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">The project covers an area of 156,000 square meters, including 35,000 square meters of green spaces, which make up 65% of the project\'s total area.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: 8.0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: 0in; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">The apartments have a unique design with high-quality finishes, and the ceiling height is 3.05 meters, which is rarely found in designs within the city centre. Each residential unit has either a terrace or a garden, which enhances your comfort and privacy.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: 8.0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: 0in; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">The project consists of 1,441 apartments distributed among 16 residential buildings designed with unique designs and creative touches, ranging from 5 to 15 floors with different apartment styles starting from 1+1 to 5+1.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: 8.0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: 0in; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">The project is located directly on the main highway in Istanbul, which is considered the lifeline of Istanbul. The distance between them is zero. It is characterized by its proximity to transportation, such as the bus, metro station, and tram station, which are 300 meters away. It is 35 minutes away from Istanbul airport and 5 minutes away from Marmaray metro station, which is the longest metro line in Istanbul, connecting the European and Asian sides of Istanbul.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: 8.0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: 0in; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">The project includes all amenities such as swimming pools, games, clubs, Turkish baths, steam rooms, saunas, and many other services that provide absolute luxury for its residents.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: 8.0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: 0in; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">The project includes a shopping mall that includes many stores with many international brands.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: 8.0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: 0in; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">There are many government and private educational services in the area for different educational stages that offer high-quality education, including Astenia Private University, Yildiz University, and many other universities in the Topkapi area, including Yeni Yuz Yil University and Medipol University.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-pagination: widow-orphan lines-together; page-break-after: avoid; mso-outline-level: 2; margin: 2.0pt 0in 0in 0in;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 13.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri Light\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #2f5496; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">Detailed Information About the Project</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0in;\" type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: 8.0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: 0in; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">A commercial centre</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; margin-top: 0in; mso-margin-bottom-alt: 8.0pt; mso-margin-top-alt: 0in; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: 150%; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">Cent